name: PKPaymentError.Code
desc: An error code that you provide to indicate problems with address or contact information on an Apple Pay sheet.

items.name: case couponCodeExpiredError
items.desc: The error code that indicates an expired coupon.

items.name: case couponCodeInvalidError
items.desc: The error code that indicates an invalid coupon.

items.name: case billingContactInvalidError
items.desc: The error code that indicates an invalid billing address or billing name.

items.name: case shippingContactInvalidError
items.desc: The error code that indicates an invalid shipping address, email, phone, or name.

items.name: case shippingAddressUnserviceableError
items.desc: The error code that indicates an unserviceable shipping address.

items.name: case unknownError
items.desc: The error code that indicates an unknown error.
